name: Insulinde
description:
Insulinde is a release set up by SicknessMP to deliver a chilled Hip/Hop release giving you great notes and ascetically pleasing beats. Working with a few friends they have provided great releases for any chilled or experimental new style music.

Beat Produced By SicknessMP
Rap Performance By Ezra Kunze & Seansation
Dj Scracth Performed By Geramar Of Mukarakat
Trumpet By Jordy Waelauruw
Artwork By Fiksidipsy
